## Mermaid Syntax Quick Reference

### Flowchart
```mermaid
flowchart TB
    A[Rectangle] --> B(Rounded)
    B --> C{Diamond}
    C -->|Yes| D[Result 1]
    C -->|No| E[Result 2]
```

### Subgraphs (for architecture)
```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph Frontend["Frontend Layer"]
        UI[React App]
        SW[Service Worker]
    end
    subgraph Backend["Backend Layer"]
        API[Express Server]
        DB[(Database)]
    end
    UI --> API
    API --> DB
```

### Sequence Diagram
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Server
    participant D as Database
    C->>S: Request
    S->>D: Query
    D-->>S: Result
    S-->>C: Response
```

### Icons (Font Awesome)
```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[fa:fa-robot Claude] --> B[fa:fa-server Backend]
    B --> C[fa:fa-database Storage]
```

